        "<ul><li>The summary should be 3-5 sentences in paragraph form<\/li><li>Things to include in a Summary Statement:<ol><li>Your current field, years of experience and career focus<\/li><li>The most relevant part of your background for the position you are applying for<\/li><li>The most impressive result you&rsquo;ve achieved in your career<\/li><li>What you offer your potential employer<\/li><\/ol><\/li><\/ul><div>Example: &ldquo;Bi-lingual Customer Service Manager with 10 years experience in a high-volume call centre. Energetic and organized team lead with a history of successful on-boarding of regional support teams. Achieved 10% reduction in refund requests and 15% increase in sales over a 2-year period. Seeking a position in a company expanding its support operations into English-speaking countries.&rdquo;<\/div>",
