    "tip":
        "<ul><li>Include grades\/percentage only if it is excellent<\/li><li>Do not include scholarships, awards or recognitions, important student projects here. We have another section for them<\/li><li>If you hold any professional qualification and have more than 10-15 years of post qualification information, it is advisable not to talk about your secondary, higher secondary and graduation in details. You can avoid giving information like school\/college name, grades, year of qualification&nbsp;<\/li><\/ul>",
