    "tipid": "14",
    "section": "51110",
    "tip":
        "<ul><li>Show your certifications if they are relevant to the desired job<\/li><li>Include not more than five most recent rectifications<\/li><li>If you have more than five certifications let the employer know that additional information is available upon request<\/li><li>Try to disclose alternative education, showing job-related training, online learning, conferences, in-services or self-directed study<\/li><\/ul>",
    "dateCreated": "2017-02-19 12:36:07",
