    "tipid": "22",
    "section": "51118",
    "tip":
        "<div><ul><li>To detail your skills use action words<\/li><li>Emphasize those skills, abilities and knowledge that meet the position requirements<\/li><li>Be selective and show only the skills relevant to the job requirements. The job description will help you to select the relevant skills<\/li><li>Write short and understandable phrases. Remember that employers love simplicity<\/li><li>All the skills you show, should be verifiable<\/li><li>Describe personal characteristics if you don&#39;t have relevant skills, such as fast learner, dependability or attention to detail<\/li><li>Do not talk about your technical skills in this section as we have a separate section for it<\/li><\/ul><\/div>",
    "dateCreated": "2017-02-19 12:36:39",
    "status": "1"
  },
